write a program to reaplace word in string using custom function

Output:

Original string
Hello I Youssef I I am YouSSef ennajar youssef _from moroco .

enter a word you want to chang it: youssef
enter a word you want to change to: ennajar


Replace with match case:
Hello I Youssef I I am YouSSef ennajar ennajar _from moroco .



Replace with dont match case:
Hello I ennajar I I am ennajar ennajar ennajar _from moroco .